N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 400.10 - Form for reporting complaint, periodic and office tests

State Regulations

The reports of complaint, periodic and office tests of
steam meter shall be made in the form designated "Complaint, Periodic and

Office Tests." [See Appendix 8-A.]
